    "According to Bates [14], access to digital technologies has transformed teacher training, offering more flexible and personalized learning.",
    "Despite these efforts, there remains a significant digital divide among teachers in terms of access doi: 10.18178/ijiet.2025.",
    "15.1.2218 Manuscript received August 21, 2024; revised September 19, 2024; accepted October 15, 2024; published January 13, 2025 and effective use of advanced research technologies.",
    "Some studies indicate that while some teachers are well-trained and use digital tools effectively, others lack the necessary skills.",
    "This variability may be due to factors such as lack of resources, generational differences, or insufficient initial training [10]."
  ]
